A really simple twitter bot that publish a tweet from a list every minute;

Config:
1)
Create a file "config.js" with the following:
--
var config = {};

config.twitter = {};
config.twitter.consumer_key = '<consumer_key>';
config.twitter.consumer_secret = '<consumer_secret>';
config.twitter.access_token_key = '<access_token_key>';
config.twitter.access_token_secret = '<access_token_secret>';
module.exports = config;

---

2)
Create a json tweet file at /data/tweets.json with an array of tweets

example:
[
  "hello world",
  "yup this is a bot",
  "such tweet much wow"
]

3)
...

4)
Profit


There is a lot to improve, this was made "Quick and Dirty"
